@startuml
title Athena Auth Client Core Session Lifecycle (Before)
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam ArrowColor #000000
skinparam defaultFontName Consolas
skinparam defaultFontColor #000000
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #FFF9C4
skinparam noteBorderColor #000000

actor "App / SDK Consumer" as Consumer #BBDEFB
component "better-auth JS SDK\n(external dependency)" as BetterAuthClient #FFE082
component "Auth Proxy Wrapper\n(app-specific glue code)" as ProxyWrapper #FFCDD2
component "Athena Auth Server\n(/api/auth/*)" as AthenaAuthServer #C8E6C9
database "Session Store" as SessionStore #D1C4E9

Consumer --> BetterAuthClient : signIn / signOut / getSession
BetterAuthClient --> ProxyWrapper : library-specific adapters
ProxyWrapper --> AthenaAuthServer : /sign-in/email\n/get-session\n/sign-out
ProxyWrapper --> AthenaAuthServer : /list-sessions\n/revoke-session(s)
AthenaAuthServer --> SessionStore : create/update/delete sessions

note right of ProxyWrapper
Core session lifecycle behavior
is spread across external SDK semantics
and custom wrappers.
end note
@enduml
